1. A computer-implemented method for compartmentalizing a virtual assistant, executed on a computing device, comprising:
 obtaining encounter information via a compartmentalized virtual assistant during a patient encounter, wherein the compartmentalized virtual assistant includes a core functionality module that verbally interacts with an encounter participant of the patient encounter, wherein the core functionality module verbally interacts with at least one of a patient and a medical professional as the encounter participant during a portion of the patient encounter; 
